snippet.title: Animal Leader - Space World 2000 Trailer [N64- Cancelled]
snippet.description:
Official trailer for Animal Leader that was shown at Space World 2000.
The title was a bizzare action game developed by Saru Brunei for N64 that later was moved to GameCube and called Cubivore in North America when it was published by Atlus.
